<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Chamado Criado com Sucesso</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <link
    href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    rel="stylesheet"
  />
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet"
  />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f3f4f6, #e5e7eb);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .success-wrapper {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 40px;
      max-width: 480px;
      width: 100%;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07);
      text-align: center;
    }

    h2 {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #111827;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #4b5563;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background-color: #6366f1;
      border: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      padding: 12px 28px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      transition: background-color 0.2s;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: white;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background-color: #4f46e5;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: white;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="success-wrapper">
    <h2>Chamado criado com sucesso!</h2>
    <p>Obrigado por registrar sua solicitação. Entraremos em contato em breve.</p>
    <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Voltar para Abrir Chamado</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
